Oridion Gets FDA Warning Letter About Quality of Purchased Items

-- B y   P a u l   V e r s c h u u r
-- 
2011-10-12T04:36:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/oridion-gets-fda-warning-letter-about-quality-of-purchased-items.html
Oridion Systems Ltd. (OSL)  said it
received a warning letter from the U.S. Food and Drug
Administration about its procedures to ensure that all purchased
or received product conforms to specified requirements.  The FDA’s observations focused on purchasing controls of
Oridion’s contract manufacturers, Oridion said today in an e-
mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Verschuur at 
 pverschuur@bloomberg.net  